Program: Omnibus
Title: Under the Volcano
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0376kn2
Last Broadcast Date: 15 September 1993
The eruption of Mount Pinatubo in the Philippines in June 1991 had devastating effects. This programme looks at the particularly bad consequences of the disaster for the Aeta community. Picture: Mount Pinatubo, Credit: Getty Images